    "body": "Hello @soragXYZ \r\n\r\nYou are getting \"Error: Bad instruction\". This probably comes from a difference of EVM version between your private network and the compiler settings your used. That might be because the contract does `address(this).balance`. There is now an opcode for that (since Istanbul), that used not to exist. The compiler probably uses it, and you networks doesn't support it.\r\n\r\nSolution: \r\n- Set your compiler to an older version of the EVM (last before istambul was petersburg)\r\n- Upgrade your private network to support [eip-1884](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1884)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
